<br>
One of the few good things I've been hearing is going to E&amp;BO is the ability to hire an NPC or terminal to sell your items for you.<br>
<br>
You place your items into the 'merchant' set a price for each and then you can go adventure or log off. When you come back you can retrieve your money or item from the merchant.<br>
<br>
This is just er....dull...and as Enan says will be neglected in favour of the easier to reach East Commons or G Fay which still caters for everyone who doesnt have luclin.<br>
